ortant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bott=
om-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"><em>really=C2=A0</em>that sort of=
 story</a>.)=C2=A0Reinventing banking is a great idea! You can make a lot o=
