sk=E2=80=94or they did so on a very limited basis. Nonetheless, the vast ma=
jority of the Rebalancing Trades involved at least one Rebalancing Broker t=
hat purchased bonds into its firm=E2=80=99s inventory.=E2=80=9D That is, us=
ually they didn=E2=80=99t buy bonds for their balance sheet, but they did f=
or Chatham because they knew they were not really at risk.</p>
