ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[4] For instance, SEC Commissioner Hester Peir=
ce, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34124062.28540=
0/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3N0YXRlbWVudC9wZWlyY2Utc3RhdGVtZW50LWZpb=
